 \; 11 AM – 3 PMFee: $115 + $15 materials feeAge: 16+ Participants: min. 
 8Learn to create beautiful designs on paper by printing with a gel plate a
 nd acrylic paint. Mixed media artist Catherine Cruz will teach you the bas
 ic skills for using this fun tool from printing textural backgrounds\, to 
